{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "journal-module-collection-2025",
		"name": "TheraAI - Journal & Mood Tracking API",
		"description": "Complete API testing for TheraAI Journal Module with AI-powered sentiment analysis\n\n## Features Tested:\n- User Authentication (prerequisite)\n- Journal Entry CRUD operations\n- AI Sentiment Analysis\n- Mood Statistics\n- Pagination\n- Authorization checks\n\n## Setup:\n1. Ensure backend is running: `uvicorn app.main:app --reload`\n2. MongoDB should be running on localhost:27017\n3. Run tests in order (authentication first)\n4. The auth token is automatically saved to collection variables\n\n## Environment Variables Used:\n- `base_url`: http://localhost:8000\n- `auth_token`: Automatically set after login\n- `journal_id`: Automatically set after creating a journal",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
